{"word":"G1944 - ἐπικατάρατος - epikatáratos - ep-ee-kat-ar'-at-os - Accursed","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπικατάρατος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epikatáratos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-kat-ar'-at-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Accursed</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சபிக்கப்பட்ட - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"accursed, execrable, exposed to divine vengeance, lying under God's curse"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2672 - καταράομαι - kataráomai - kat-ar-ah'-om-ahee/2672\">G2672</a>; <i>imprecated</i>, that is, <i>execrable:</i> - accursed.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1944/1944\">G1944</a>, <a href=\"#/G2671/2671\">G2671</a>, <a href=\"#/G2672/2672\">G2672</a>, <a href=\"#/G685/685\">G685</a>, <a href=\"#/G686/686\">G686</a>, <a href=\"#/G687/687\">G687</a>"}]}